01:09:43,370 --> 01:09:44,950
...estrume inferno...

662
01:09:45,040 --> 01:09:46,790
...Inferno de gelo...

663
01:09:46,870 --> 01:09:48,370
...Inferno de puxar a língua

664
01:09:48,450 --> 01:09:53,290
